title: Border Battle Football Feast!
description: PA & Charch at BWWs Savage! Show kicks off with Chad Greenway on site, followed by former Vikings receiver Matthew Hatchette making an appearance to end the first hour! The great Randy Moss called in midway through, and the rest is filled with football talkers into the weekend before Monday's border battle!
